Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.75,0:00:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《人间失格》中有各式各样的女性登场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而太宰自身也与众多女性传过绯闻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如在镰仓引起殉情骚动的田部缔子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时太宰生还 只有缔子送了命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有由井伏鳟二做媒结婚的石原美知子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为小说《斜阳》的执笔提供了素材的情妇太田静子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.40,0:00:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一同殉情的情妇山崎富荣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这激情而繁杂的女性关系之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有过这样一段轶事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在太宰27岁时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时其姘居的妻子小山初代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在太宰住院治疗药物中毒之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红杏出墙与太宰的义弟犯下了错误
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事对太宰以及《人间失格》带来了怎样的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.91,0:00:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因名作 更显青涩 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.38,0:00:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看 人间失格最终话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（1936年）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…请问这里是大叶先生府上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是上门推销的 还请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堀木
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是堀木吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 亏你竟能找到这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找你有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的旧友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那头是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 有点原因
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公 别站在门口说话呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人家进屋吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看来气色不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第几次？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢 几年没见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找你有两件要事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两件？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正没啥好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你画的漫画卖得还挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 上茶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还是备点酒菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我时间不多 酒就免了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 别在意嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你的洁癖治好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前动不动就洗手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你是来勾起我痛苦回忆的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了她 活得总算有点人样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是个好女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她可是信赖的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信赖的天才？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这样的我 她也毫无疑心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世间不就是人的集合吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她一说 我才发觉世间不过就是人的集合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.71,0:04:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐惧消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没什么大不了的 世间这玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 又喝酒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是处女？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没礼貌 突然说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我戒酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你肯嫁给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你就玷污了无人经由的处女地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰到她 我便获得了重生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她才是我的圣母玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩一起租下这间房
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人一同过活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱的事我来想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想什么办法呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要画出卖座的漫画就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你下楼去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要进这间房
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.87,0:07:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护美子 我什么都做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次想为了自己以外的他人而活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于想通了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世间渴望知道你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定能成为日本第一的小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是报酬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原稿我拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作间隙和她去看看电影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也去银座吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许这就是幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你漫画的读者 很快就会追求更多刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你还没看过我的作品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是身经百战的小丑 别把我看扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是编的 什么我都画得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也算半真半假吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 怎样都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你今后 很快就没有卖点了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 确实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今后我打算画点真正想画的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:09:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然活少了点 总算能赚点生活费
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没跟你喝酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 真不像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楼下负责人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 今天是截稿日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是别喝酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝一阵子他就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不好吧 到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我高兴啊 你会来看我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 鱼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是煮了豆子 很快便好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是个好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你来这有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前天我偶然碰见了“比目鱼”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是你老爸已经去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:11:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个月前 好像是胃溃疡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你说过在当上名画家之前不回津轻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也知道你恨你老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过至少该回去上柱香 才算有点人性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么人性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么…人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人性什么的我早就舍弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还说什么 “人性”？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是想让老爸承认自己而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种人不就是个政客吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他已经不在人世了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶藏 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样都无所谓 对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 世间 甚至自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有她在 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等着 我这就去拿水来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶藏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也是地狱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了这里还有别的地狱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是时候 不过我还是得告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞？慢着 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 现在要我和那女人独处…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不得不下地狱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我入伍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入伍…参军了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就去报到 得打点行装
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 堀木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 别走 求你别走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是艺术家吗 为什么要去打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界正在崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许正因是艺术家 感受才更深刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶藏 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做人最后的界限是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因自己饥饿就夺人口粮的那不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你夺走了女人的生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有杀人 没有杀人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 听着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确实夺走了人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只是遵从对方的意志 这还算好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 今后可不能再这么天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都不再为人 畜生的时代即将来临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该来的总会来的 我就先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把世上的人都杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你保重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…说也是白说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:15:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救你 我怎么做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实根本没有活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.17,0:16:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的漫画 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西居然卖得出去 早觉得蹊跷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为了从他那接到活 为了让我有活干
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美子本该是我的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 一旦起了疑心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:17:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那无比肮脏的感情便会占据脑海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…无法回到从前了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身上缺少某种人的特质
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…做人的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胃已经清洗过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这位病人我们这里治不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:19:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说只能送去精神病院了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几时能出院呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好再留三天看看情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能提前一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这么说也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放着他不管 只会重复自杀未遂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 净给人添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来要是阿叶死了 你会少很多好处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜也能猜个大概
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八成是津轻那边还在给你汇阿叶的生活费吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种人渣 我不管还谁管
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底谁是人渣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所认识的阿叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又诚实 又乖巧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不喝酒的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…即便是喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是一个神一般的好孩子呐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候多时了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要治什么病呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很痛苦 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我点能好过些的药
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后 我们永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.20,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
